{"tid":1243991,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"去餐廳同時叫兩碟一樣 會難食左定好食左?","createTime":"2019-06-19T16:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T12:16:00.000Z","uid":12034,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7858c93d24f8bc9664f5763acce6b66b8670eef1","tid":1243991,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"成日諗一個問題<br />\n講緊一般情況 一般餐廳下<br />\n即係我嗌楊洲炒飯/菜芯炒牛肉咁先算<br />\n同枱條友又同時叫同我一樣<br />\n張單入到廚房 更係兩份一齊炒啦<br />\n咁結果會好食左 多料左 <br />\n定係更加求其 炒飯兜兩兜 因為兩份料一齊炒<br />\n而變得更加難食?"},{"pid":"e6c5270a7b3ed8027565f9664e88714360e9b1b5","tid":1243991,"uid":181092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"一碟炒應該好食d"},{"pid":"ff22be71997943ab06f76745351b37b99ffdab3e","tid":1243991,"uid":111087,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"飲食唔係1+1=2<br />\n兩個分量唔係得於兩個一份<br />\n要微調當中分量"},{"pid":"e2502e89d538b232136fd447d211138d79834184","tid":1243991,"uid":69528,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"得返2/3碟而淡味左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28dd9d96d729082a9b2e8492a94d7cfdadd1ee4","tid":1243991,"uid":35107,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"細碟咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad3dd81d9bda7155adc807eb32084caabc022c6","tid":1243991,"uid":58750,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"好似佢落油咁 <br />\n唔通佢落足兩倍油咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cff9fa5bc49a223377671d702742f0a9230e28d","tid":1243991,"uid":181092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"幾個份量有時炒唔混d調味"},{"pid":"9eac261c81761be52f997ff077a2ad87fc8aaec1","tid":1243991,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"試過兩碟炒麵 兩碟都係滿到瀉<br />\n又試過 炒牛河 明顯係1.5份變2份<br />\n想知廚房佬點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b55f0c2d1c9ccafda03e4dffcee107e7577b75f","tid":1243991,"uid":235174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"Google面試問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9461deca7e6894740bfd2d1b7dfb073c8095a910","tid":1243991,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"一碟份量同啲料有幾多其實有standard <br />\n係其中一碟可能分嗰陣分多咗小小<br />\n份量應該出入唔大<br />\n<br />\n味道好咗定差咗依樣真係好難講<br />\n睇廚師技術同落調味嘅份量㗎姐<br />\n就算得一張單都可以係比上一次好/差咗㗎"},{"pid":"78eb648c4fb3ed03688799dbb8c501ebd33720d7","tid":1243991,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:44:42.000Z","msg":"正常酒樓有人執碼,材料既總量冇變,一齊落獲但係分碟一定唔平圴"},{"pid":"9ee0ff2b82ec7064a66e52a8413ca0a0efd25bd6","tid":1243991,"uid":106326,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"一定係難食左<br />\n無論西餐定中餐<br />\n當所有份量一樣<br />\n同一隻鑊去炒 材料多左一倍的話平均受熱不足<br />\n炒出黎唔均勻無鑊氣<br />\n而且時間長左會令食物overcook"},{"pid":"d67de294207ef1fef8b1bf6c37bc00ef092069e6","tid":1243991,"uid":230198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"兩碟應該細碟左但好味左<br />\n<br />\n炒粉麵飯, <br />\n炒一碟要落多d料先炒得起<br />\n兩碟就可以share起鑊油 無咁油 特別炒河"},{"pid":"ea40131ffa2b4f3004a2306b43edece198f1820c","tid":1243991,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"成日變左1.25碟+0.75碟"},{"pid":"171ad0236d489d9a781fa026d4584c0708ef1e74","tid":1243991,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:10:00.000Z","msg":"正常一定係一份好食d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e6ad050b4daa2d56222c03fd76f054010cfa65","tid":1243991,"uid":23828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:13:01.000Z","msg":"試